 commutes with 
\begin_inset Formula $\exp\left[-\frac{i}{2}\lambda^{\prime}\hat{P}_{D}\hat{\sigma}_{y}\right]\exp\left[\sum_{i}\frac{\gamma_{iD}}{\omega_{i}}\hat{P}_{D}\left(\hat{b}^{\dagger}-\hat{b}\right)\right]$
